Wete Portal Enhancement Plan
Current Understanding
The Wete Portal is a Laravel-based application focused on waste management and circular economy. The system already has:
Basic admin functionality for content management
Models for various entities like News, Content, Pages, Waste Locations
Controllers for both frontend and admin
Bootstrap-based styling
Enhancement Plan
1. Admin Panel Restructuring
Create a new sidebar layout with two main sections:
Main Website Management
Waste Management System
Shared features (accessible outside the sections):
Dashboard
User Management
Settings
Profile
2. Frontend Design Improvements
Implement modern design elements with animations
Add scroll animations using AOS (Animate On Scroll)
Design beautiful card components with hover effects
Create a cohesive color scheme
Implement responsive templates for admin-entered content
3. Implementation Steps
Phase 1: Admin Panel Restructuring
Update the admin layout with the new sidebar structure
Create new blade components for the sectioned sidebar
Reorganize admin routes to match the new structure
Ensure proper permissions for each section
Phase 2: Frontend Enhancements
Implement AOS animations for scroll effects
Design new card components with hover effects
Create templates for displaying admin-entered content
Implement a cohesive color scheme throughout the site
Phase 3: Testing and Refinement
Test admin functionality
Test frontend responsiveness
Fix any issues
Refine animations and transitions